{"tid":913234,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"庫克:蘋果正開發自駕車軟件系統","createTime":"2018-11-23T08:49:15.000Z","updateTime":"2018-11-23T08:49:15.000Z","uid":28765,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"893144ae85e41d864228a1a68a4ef7f8de78ae10","tid":913234,"uid":28765,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-23T08:49:15.000Z","msg":"蘋果行政總裁庫克透露，蘋果正在開發自動駕駛汽車軟件系統。<br />\n<br />\n早前一直有傳蘋果對汽車領域產生興趣，而庫克上述的表態，是首次承認蘋果在汽車領域的布局。他接受外電訪問時稱，蘋果正在研發自主系統，並強調公司的目光現時主要集中於軟件系統上。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://www2.hkej.com/landing/mobArticle2/id/1999114/庫克%3A蘋果正開發自駕車軟件系統\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww2.hkej.com%2Flanding%2FmobArticle2%2Fid%2F1999114%2F%E5%BA%AB%E5%85%8B%253A%E8%98%8B%E6%9E%9C%E6%AD%A3%E9%96%8B%E7%99%BC%E8%87%AA%E9%A7%95%E8%BB%8A%E8%BB%9F%E4%BB%B6%E7%B3%BB%E7%B5%B1&d=1hC2mXRqFVwtGDzsKQdeR9ibCDpHM%2Bj7ejEBwfn5qys%3D&h=6c8d642c\" target=\"_blank\">http://www2.hkej.com/landing/mobArticle2/id/1999114/庫克%3A蘋果正開發自駕車軟件系統</a>"}]}